and <br>
2) Chant: self end regen that drain pow/time<br>
and<br>
3) castable self buff (15min dur) that is an end redux for styles<br>
<br>
This combo is just like the friar and just a bit diff from wardens (both 1.5 spec melee/support hybrids) who have castable self haste.<br>
<br>
Cant use self end regen AND a new/improved dmg add (hpoing for 9 dps and 1500 range) at same time but we will almost always have an end redux self buff up.<br>
<br>
OR<br>
<br>
1) Shout (30 s dur/3min recast): self haste, self end regen that drains pow/time, and self end redux for styling<br>
<br>
Just like friars but compressed into 1 shout<br>
<br>
Can be used in synchronicity with a new and improved dmg add but we will not usually have end redux buff up.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
One of those 2 paths with the new/improved dmg add, new support based RA (along BoF, SoS lines), lvl 34 dd on 1500 range, lvl 44 dd on new resist (spirit?), fix skipped pulses.  This will fix skalds.<br>
<br>
Thats MHO. <p>Albron<br>
Level 50 Norse Skald<br>
HOOKED on speed!<br>
